::DrillBit::

"Ok. I'll come down there," DrillBit replyes to Ram-Jet.
"We'll discuss the Alliance later," he says to DarkFate and Killfest.
As he walks out he gives KitKat3 a kiss.
"You want to join us, honey?"
She had been acting a little weird lately, when he had a chance he would
take her to the med bay and have her checked out.
